snippet.title: Star Wars High Republic writer plays victim card! Lucasfilm war rumors get a little weird!?
snippet.description:
Lot's of Star Wars The High Republic and video game news to go over! Apparently, if you don't agree with the writers politically, you're an evil person! Also, the rumors of a ideological battle at Lucasflm are getting a little ridiculous! 

Shout out to @Geeks + Gamers for the Rey Lesner photo!
